helpM:
[>help -M]: Shows this message!
[>play]: Plays music
[>add <yt_link>]: Adds music to the queue (YT links only)
[>queue]: Shows the queue
[>v+]: Increase volume
[>v-]: Decreases volume

For more help options, type ">help -H"
helpH:
[>help -H]: Shows help command list
[>help -G]: Shows General command list
[>help -MD]: Shows Moderator commands
[>help -O]: Shows owner only commands
[>help -M]: Shows music commands
[>help -F]: Shows Fun commands
